{"title":"调单帐号存活度分析","name":"调单帐号存活度分析","img":"","bz":"分析已调账户的交易时间区间和实际交易天数、交易详情\n活跃账户的最后余额（账户最新余额，可酌情冻结）\n非活跃账户的最后出账对手（疑似替代卡，可调取）\n可根据最后两笔出款交易时间间隔判断账号是否活跃\n可变条件设置说明：\n最后交易距导入日期的时间间隔：默认值90天（可在结果表头右键修改条件），以该时间间隔值划分活跃与非活跃，值越大则活跃度越低；\n最后两次出款时间间隔：默认值0-100天（可在结果表头右键修改条件），值越大则活跃度越低。\n注：本模型数据侧重时效性，需要导入数据为近期调取才能保证结果准确性。","ctype":"12","version":"datacube_20221010_A1538","script":"{\"cloneRel\":{\"table-13\":{\"from\":\"table-2\",\"to\":\"table-13\"},\"table-24\":{\"from\":\"table-7\",\"to\":\"table-24\"},\"table-41\":{\"from\":\"table-2\",\"to\":\"table-41\"}},\"tables\":{\"table-13\":{\"fieldWidth\":{\"0;jy_mc__max__06607_1\":78,\"0;jy_zkh\":160,\"0;sj\":160,\"0;jy_je\":160,\"0;jy_ye\":160,\"0;jdbz\":160,\"0;ds_mc__max__70959_1\":114,\"0;ds_zh\":160,\"0;ip\":160,\"0;mac\":160,\"0;zysm\":160,\"0;cube_imp_ort_time__max__92321_1\":147},\"sortName\":\"jy_je\",\"data\":{\"total\":0,\"isError\":false,\"lazy\":true,\"rows\":[],\"isEncrypt\":false,\"historyTotal\":0},\"whereSql\":{\"userSql\":\"\",\"executeSql\":\"\\\"jdbz\\\" in ('出')\\n\\nand ( \\\"ds_zh\\\"  is not null and  \\\"ds_zh\\\" <>'')\\n\"},\"title\":\"出账流水\",\"extend\":[],\"tableType\":\"cube\",\"sortOrder\":\"desc\",\"x\":2028,\"name\":\"1\",\"tableId\":\"table-13\",\"y\":1111,\"where\":{\"jdbz\":{\"field\":\"jdbz\",\"title\":\"借贷标志\",\"type\":\"char\",\"attr\":{\"charL\":\"\",\"multiequals\":\"出\",\"charU\":\"\",\"isExcept\":false}},\"ds_zh\":{\"field\":\"ds_zh\",\"title\":\"对手账号\",\"type\":\"char\",\"attr\":{\"charL\":\"\",\"multiequals\":\"\",\"exp\":[{\"bds\":\" and (<1> is not null and <1><>'')\",\"cname\":\"非空值\"}],\"charU\":\"\",\"isExcept\":false}}}},\"table-24\":{\"fieldWidth\":{\"0;jy_mc__max__01677_3\":219,\"0;jy_zkh\":200,\"0;jy_je__sum__64806_3\":80,\"0;cunt__30985_2__sum__86646_3\":80,\"0;sj__min__74990_3\":160,\"0;sj__max__93724_3\":160,\"0;excol___2\":140,\"0;excol___3\":297,\"0;excol___1\":115,\"0;cunt__57673_3\":169,\"0;excol___4\":140,\"0;cube_imp_ort_time__max__37150_3\":147},\"sortName\":\"excol_